"The secret of my success is that we have gone to exceptional

118
00:06:23.444 --> 00:06:27.388
lengths to hire the best people in the world.

119
00:06:27.388 --> 00:06:28.752
" -Steve Jobs.

120
00:06:28.752 --> 00:06:30.598
Hiring new people should not be taken lightly,

121
00:06:30.598 --> 00:06:33.502
in fact I take hiring very seriously indeed.

